    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. There are several noticeable cosmetic blemishes, including minor dents on the exterior and some staining on the interior upholstery. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but the engine is no longer as quiet as it once was, and the suspension feels a bit loose, suggesting that some parts will need replacement in the near future. While it doesn't require immediate major repairs to stay on the road, a buyer should expect to invest in ongoing maintenance to keep it in good working order.",
