    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for a driver looking for reliable transportation without the premium price of a showroom-quality car. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some minor paint fading on the hood and roof, consistent with its age. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain fully functional. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and handles well, though it may require some minor maintenance items in the near future. It is a practical, honest vehicle for anyone prioritizing utility over perfect aesthetics.",
