    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. It honestly breaks my heart a little to put my pride and joy up for sale, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute gem. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every weekend, and serviced like clockwork. She looks and drives just like she did the day she rolled off the lot. Aside from one tiny, barely-there mark that you\u2019d need a magnifying glass to find, she\u2019s practically perfect. If you\u2019re looking for a car that\u2019s been loved with a capital L, this is the one. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 48500.0,
