      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a masterclass in precision engineering. This specimen features a blueprinted powerplant optimized for peak volumetric efficiency, paired with a bespoke ECU remap that sharpens transient throttle response while maintaining the integrity of the forged internals. The chassis has been enhanced with high-durometer bushings and reinforced subframe mounting points to eliminate deflection under high lateral loads, ensuring surgical turn-in. Meticulously maintained with rigorous thermal cycling protocols and 3,000-mile synthetic fluid intervals, the drivetrain exhibits zero parasitic drag and delivers linear power through a crisp, short-throw linkage. This is a turnkey, concours-ready machine for the discerning pilot who demands mechanical purity and uncompromising structural rigidity.",
      "price": 49500.0,
